'''Yohann Kouam''' (wavutse 1982), ni umukinnyi wa firime [[Ubufaransa|w’Abafaransa]] kimwe na producer<ref>http://www.spla.pro/file.person.yohann-kouam.28651.html</ref>, umwanditsi wa sinema ukomoka [[Kameruni|muri Kameruni.]]  Yakoze firime ngufi zamamaye cyane<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/directors/yohann-kouam/</ref>. 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yohann numuyobozi wa firime y' [[ubufaransa]].  Se ni umucungamari naho nyina ni umunyamahoteri<ref>https://www.safirhdf.fr/auteursid.php?auteurid=41</ref>. 

== Umwuga ==
Yize gutunganya firime muri Institut des arts de diffusion  i Buruseli, hanyuma yiga Ubuhinduzi mu [[Bufaransa]]<ref>http://africultures.com/personnes/?no=28651</ref>.  Nyuma yaje kuba umufasha wigisha mumashuri yisumbuye gutanga amasomo yindimi<ref>http://www.africine.org/film/retour-le-real-yohann-kouam/16605</ref>. 

Muri 2007, Kouam yakoze film ngufi ''Fragments de vie'' . Yakiriwe neza, yakoze film ya kabiri ngufi ya ''Les dimanches de Léa'' mu 2010<ref>https://www.senscritique.com/contact/Yohann_Kouam/1703773</ref>.  Yaje gukora filime ngufi ''Yagarutse'' mu 2013,  yamenyekanye ku rwego mpuzamahanga. Muri 2016, yakoze film ''Kuva San Francisco hamwe nUrukundo'' <ref>https://www.programme-tv.net/cinema/6537577-le-retour/</ref>.

